            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "內地首季房地產開發投資按年跌9.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國家統計局公布，今年首季全國房地產開發投資按年跌9.9%，較首2個月擴大0.1個百分點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">首季新建商品房銷售面積按年跌3%，較首2個月收窄2.1個百分點。銷售額跌2.1%，收窄0.5個百分點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">數據又顯示，首季房地產開發企業到位資金按年跌3.7%，新開工面積跌24.4%；首2月分別跌3.6%和29.6%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14858349-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e6%88%bf%e5%9c%b0%e7%94%a2%e9%96%8b%e7%99%bc%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e8%b7%8c9-9-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20231108_FI_source_licensed_China-Property_shutterstock_704.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-16 10:40:40",
